ZH: 只有努力才能取得成功。
EN: Only by working hard can we achieve success.

ZH: 只有实践才能掌握技能。
EN: Only through practice can we master the skills.

ZH: 只有毅力才能战胜困难。
EN: Only with perseverance can we overcome difficulties.

ZH: 只有合作才能取得共同进步。
EN: Only through cooperation can we make progress together.

ZH: 只有付出才能收获。
EN: Only through giving can we receive.

ZH: 只有耐心才能等待成功。
EN: Only with patience can we wait for success.

ZH: 只有信任才能建立良好关系。
EN: Only through trust can we build a good relationship.

ZH: 只有倾听才能理解他人。
EN: Only by listening can we understand others.

ZH: 只有认真才能学到东西。
EN: Only by being serious can we learn things.

ZH: 只有宽容才能和解。
EN: Only through forgiveness can we reconcile.

ZH: 只有敬畏自然才能保护环境。
EN: Only by respecting nature can we protect the environment.

ZH: 只有关爱弱者才能建立和谐社会。
EN: Only by caring for the weak can we build a harmonious society.

ZH: 只有节制才能保持健康。
EN: Only through moderation can we maintain good health.

ZH: 只有取舍才能做明智选择。
EN: Only by making choices can we make wise decisions.

ZH: 只有追寻梦想才能实现人生价值。
EN: Only by pursuing dreams can we fulfill our life's purpose.

ZH: 只有重视教育才能提升国家实力。
EN: Only by valuing education can we enhance national strength.

ZH: 只有无私奉献才能带来幸福。
EN: Only through selfless giving can we bring happiness.

ZH: 只有尊重差异才能促进和谐共存。
EN: Only by respecting differences can we promote harmonious coexistence.

ZH: 只有改变自己才能改变命运。
EN: Only by changing ourselves can we change our destiny.

ZH: 只有求助才能克服困难。
EN: Only by seeking help can we overcome challenges.
